collection.name: Sappy Seals
collection.description:
Sappy Seals is community-led project focused on metaverse expansion and a growing ecosystem

Holder count is not accurate due to staking. An up to date count can be found at our website: https://sappyseals.io/

Sappy Seals offers: 

- The open world cross-community Pixlverse & Pixl Pets

- Marketplace for exclusive metaverse items

- Rarity-based staking for the PIXL utility token

Join them on their cool conquest by joining the Discord http://discord.gg/zy2dfyMKwE
